userPromptForThisRevision: Full featured dashboard with lots of data sources including some customizable ones, and tonnes of synthesis and visualization.

imageAssets.description: A sleek, abstract logo icon for a 'Dashboard to the Internet'. Style: modern flat design with a subtle blue gradient, evoking connectivity and data. Subject: A stylized representation of interconnected nodes or a dynamic data stream forming an abstract globe shape. Dominant colors: shades of Bootstrap primary blue (approx #0d6efd), with accents of a lighter cyan or teal. Background: transparent for versatile use, or a very light grey (#f8f9fa) if transparency is an issue. Clean lines, professional, tech-forward aesthetic. Should be suitable for a small header logo (e.g., 32x32 or 40x40 pixels).
imageAssets.purpose: Header logo for the dashboard, to be displayed next to the 'Dashboard to the Internet' title. The target HTML path will be /generated_images/placeholder_logo.png
